# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# BHAGAT TECH SOLUTIONS — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your real values
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Supabase ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get these from: https://supabase.com → Your Project → Settings → API
#
# SUPABASE_URL          → Project URL  (e.g. https://xxxx.supabase.co)
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY → service_role secret key (NOT the anon key)
#
# ⚠️  NEVER prefix SERVICE_ROLE_KEY with NEXT_PUBLIC_ — server-side only!
SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-id.supabase.co
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-secret-key

# ── Web3Forms (contact form email forwarding) ───────────────
# Get your key at: https://web3forms.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=YOUR_WEB3FORMS_KEY

# ── EmailJS (Gmail integration for contact form) ────────────
# Sign up at: https://emailjs.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_EMAILJS_SERVICE_ID=YOUR_SERVICE_ID
NEXT_PUBLIC_EMAILJS_TEMPLATE_ID=YOUR_TEMPLATE_ID
NEXT_PUBLIC_EMAILJS_PUBLIC_KEY=YOUR_PUBLIC_KEY

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# WhatsApp redirect works with ZERO configuration.
# The number is hardcoded in lib/contactConfig.js
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
